title Retirement

user->UI: Click Spin
UI->logic: Spin message
logic->logic: compute roll
logic->logic: reach end of board
logic->retire calc: retire played
retire calc->retire calc: add early retrement bonus
retire calc->retire calc: add bonus for dependants
retire calc->retire calc: add bonus for action cards
loop for each house owned
   retire calc->UI: request spin to determine price
   user->UI: Click spin
   UI->retire calc: Spin message
   retire calc->retire calc: Sell house based on spin
end
retire calc->logic: return retirement money
logic->logic: remove player from active set
logic->UI: turn over/status update
user->UI: acknowledge turn end
UI->logic: ack. message
logic->logic: next player
